# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者做生意嘅時候，為咗避免損失繼續擴大而及時放棄或者賣出，停止虧損（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop loss
<eg>
yue:隻股票跌咗三成，我決定止蝕賣出。 (zek3 gu2 piu3 dit3 zo2 saam1 sing4, ngo5 kyut3 ding6 zi2 sit6 maai6 ceot1.)
eng:The stock has dropped 30%, so I decided to cut my losses and sell it. [end of text]


